body.name: 23”L*11”W*25”H Rustic End Table with Charging Station & USB Ports, Entryway Narrow Side Console Table for Living Room, Nightstand with Fabric Drawer Storage Shelf Sofa Table for Bedroom, Brown
features: [Robust Durable Construction]: 1. We are a professional furniture factory for many years, with professional craftsmanship and reliable suppliers. With these advantages, we choose premium thickened steel pipe and harder composite panel, and the product has a load capacity of 260lb or more. 2. The drawers of the rustic style are made of non-woven fabric, which is stronger and more durable than the general material with increased thickness.

[More Than Practical and Stylish]: With a charging station on the back, 2 USB ports and 2 outlets, we designed this rustic vintage product to be suitable for a variety of home scenarios. For example, a cost effective small TV stand with plug-in, or a helpful console table at the entrance or an ample sofa side table on living room.

[Ample Storage Space]: Measuring 22.8 "L*11.4 "W, the two-tier fabric drawers can hold home decor or anything you need to have on hand. The lower level features two non-woven drawers of thickened material, which are vintage in style and also provide you with storage space from dust.

[Friendly, with Safety in Mind]: 1. The four corners of the desktop are designed with rounded corners to protect children and avoid bumps. 2. Equipped with 4 adjustable feet to help adjust the height of the surface if the ground is uneven. Also the foot pad can avoid scratches and wear on the floor.

[Reinforced Packaging & Easy to Assembly]: For safe transportation, we use thickened and strengthened packaging materials. With all accessories and instructions are in the package, very easy to follow instructions and simple to assemble.
[After Sale Service]: For any other help, please feel free to contact us via messaging. We will reply within 24 hrs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price
reviews.reviewText: Nice looking and does what I need. I was a little surprised at first that the drawers are reinforced fabric but then considering the price that makes sense.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These night stands are everything id hoped for. I love the charging station most. Easy to assemble.. great item. Will recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good side table
reviews.reviewText: Important to note that the drawers are a felt material, they look like wood in the photo but they are soft drawers. I’m so glad I read the reviews and saw that, because otherwise I would have been disappointed. However, it looks really good in the space, the charging port works well, and for the price, I don’t think you can beat it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Looks nice, feels flimsy
reviews.reviewText: Overall, it was easy to assemble and looks nice. But don't put too much weight on the top, it feels a bit flimsy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: What I liked about this stand is that it is not a bulky piece of furniture. I use it as an nightstand. It has a charger and an AC outlet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is Good!
reviews.reviewText: I use this for a nightstand, and I love it. It is kind of small but pay attention to the measurements before you buy it. People complain about the cardboard drawers, but they hold everything I need. I'm not putting bricks in there.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2022
reviews.reviewText: This has to be one of the cheapest most versatile bedside table I have ever had. Comes in a small box very easy to put together. If you can't put this together you should not operate doors call for help. This is so very well designed for the most any material can yield not much more. For todays apartment transient population a good buy

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This bedside table is very flimsy and should not be used in a young kids room. It won’t last more then one or two days. The drawers are very hard to open and the are constructed from very thin cardboard its easy to assemble but that’s the only positive comment I can make.
